OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FGenerally dry across the area
OL,6,Fwith bright or sunny spells, though
OL,7,Frather cloudy at times, especially
OL,8,Facross the north of the region. Winds
OL,9,Fmostly light across the region.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FPlenty of clear spells going
OL,12,Finto the evening and remaining dry
OL,13,Fwith light winds. Perhaps some
OL,14,Fcloudier conditions developing near
OL,15,Fthe Kentish coast later in the night.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FA bright day with plenty of
OL,18,Fhazy sunshine, although perhaps
OL,19,Fbecoming cloudier later. Risk of some
OL,20,Fisolated thundery showers during the
OL,21,Fevening and overnight. Winds light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
