OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,6,Fand bright for Tuesday and Thursday
OL,7,Fwith sunny spells, though cloudier on
OL,8,FWednesday with a few spots of rain.
OL,9,FBreezy at times and turning warmer,
OL,10,Fperhaps hot by Thursday.
